resources.string:
Foodine will help you to live healthy in easy way. You can calculate your foods nutrition based on your recipes and plan your meal for next day. So you can find out how much calories to take and burn everyday based on your condition and ideal goals! 

Run out of ingredients to cook your desire food? Foodine also equipped by shopping list, so it will help you to remind what should you buy next time! 

To get started, input your profile details and we will determine best ideal goals for you. We will inform your daily calories needed based on that, so you can easily track your food and reach your goals soon.
Write your question or feedback here. We\'d love to hear from you
